CHAPTER 3 â€“ SharePoint Online Architecture (Complete Breakdown)

SharePoint Online is built on Multi-tenant cloud architecture.

Layers of Architecture:

1. Tenant Level

Your Microsoft 365 subscription

Contains all SharePoint sites

Managed by Global Admin & SharePoint Admin



