CHAPTER 28 â€“ SharePoint REST API (Full Reference)

REST Endpoint:

https://tenant.sharepoint.com/_api/

Common Operations

âœ” Get List Items

/_api/web/lists/getbytitle('ListName')/items

âœ” Create Item

POST /_api/web/lists/getbytitle('ListName')/items

âœ” Get Libraries

/_api/web/lists?$filter=BaseTemplate eq 101

âœ” Upload File

/_api/web/GetFolderByServerRelativeUrl('/Library')/Files/add(...)

âœ” User Info

/_api/web/currentuser


