CHAPTER 36 â€“ Backup & Recovery in SharePoint Online

SharePoint Online automatically maintains:

âœ” Recycle Bin

93 days retention

Stage 1 + Stage 2 recycle bin


âœ” Version History

Unlimited (if enabled)

Restore older versions individually


âœ” Files Restore

Restore entire library to previous time

Useful after ransomware attack


âœ” No manual backup required

Microsoft manages:

Datacenter redundancy

Geo-redundant storage

Server failover systems


Admins can use:

3rd party backups (AvePoint / Veeam / Datto)



